{"id": 1996, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X博世家电】你对你用过的厨房到底有什么不满？", "description": "工欲善其事，必先利其器，它们可能是你成为大厨路上的最大阻碍。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7432, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171106202100UqGsR5wHodeag3xF.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-24T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 250882, "content": "油太多，不想进去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192684}, {"id": 250887, "content": "不够宽敞\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125548}, {"id": 250888, "content": "用过一个比自己家还大的厨房，做了一碗泡面", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81675}, {"id": 250891, "content": "水难收拾，油烟机撞头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139257}, {"id": 250894, "content": "能放下两个锅就没了...一个未来大厨...额...算了...还是放一个锅吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192713}, {"id": 252689, "content": "开车啊，聚餐啊，都爱玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173153}, {"id": 250898, "content": "痛苦啦啦啦啦健健康康快快乐乐健健康康快快乐乐健健康康快快乐乐考虑考虑兔兔天图腾图我DJ吐了口唾沫小心翼翼小心翼翼无聊通途了呕吐咯哦哦天咯哦图 Joe 在卧佛舞台我母兔子舞台我想我哦。快乐my走咯都克服图", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120595}, {"id": 250899, "content": "东西放不下，放了找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674546}, {"id": 252691, "content": "在成都旅行，一边看手机一边走路，掉坑里了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 250900, "content": "油腻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173239}, {"id": 250901, "content": "油烟机，老是要滴油", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950816}, {"id": 250902, "content": "太油腻，清洗不方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108191}, {"id": 250903, "content": "油烟清理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191451}, {"id": 250904, "content": "手残党哪哪都不喜欢，哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122421}, {"id": 250905, "content": "打理起来困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 286987}, {"id": 250906, "content": "空间太小，本大厨发挥不出真实水平", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111809}, {"id": 251162, "content": "1", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120595}, {"id": 250907, "content": "怕油溅到自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191459}, {"id": 251675, "content": "那里都是油?都不知道从哪下手了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198375}, {"id": 250908, "content": "自动搞卫生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108190}, {"id": 250909, "content": "没有油烟机 不能忍，太呛人了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156643}, {"id": 250910, "content": "地方太小了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156827}, {"id": 250911, "content": "厨房面积局限了我的拳脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191473}, {"id": 250912, "content": "不够大！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007397}, {"id": 250913, "content": "油烟味儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869045}, {"id": 250914, "content": "装了一个没有洗碗功能的消毒柜，不知道有什么用？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107227}, {"id": 253218, "content": "不喜欢打扫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206829}, {"id": 250915, "content": "厨房是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151252}, {"id": 250916, "content": "灶台料理台全都是统一高度，就算是定制的装修时厨房的柜子台面高度大多都是80公分到90公分吧，个子高的人做个饭腰能断！抽油烟机撞头简直……", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818157}, {"id": 250917, "content": "油烟太重，抽油烟机不给力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192764}, {"id": 250918, "content": "我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192767}, {"id": 250920, "content": "空调要么太冷，要么太热", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 250921, "content": "调料罐太多太杂乱，每次要用要找半天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107202}, {"id": 250922, "content": "抽油烟机马力不行，做顿饭眼镜上糊一层油", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614051}, {"id": 250923, "content": "油烟机怎么拆下来洗的?给的说明书还是别的油烟机的，₍₍ (̨̡ ‾᷄ᗣ‾᷅ )̧̢ ₎₎麻烦Ծ‸Ծ走点心啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802667}, {"id": 250924, "content": "烧完菜不仅要洗碗 还要擦各种油腻台面", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140460}, {"id": 250925, "content": "电视机开机慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107206}, {"id": 250927, "content": "首先你得有一套房", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040621}, {"id": 250928, "content": "在北京合租 同租的人吃过的碗放几天不洗，占着洗碗池", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964391}, {"id": 250929, "content": "夏天做饭好热啊……中式厨房又不能装空调。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024356}, {"id": 250930, "content": "不喜欢厨房油腻腻的，而且厨房东西杂，收拾好了也看起来没那么整齐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192821}, {"id": 250931, "content": "时间久了，哪里都油腻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 250933, "content": "冰箱不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168185}, {"id": 250935, "content": "不下厨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 250936, "content": "水池下方的橱柜异味大！大理石台面 时间一久都表面黏黏的难清洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905397}, {"id": 250937, "content": "卫生难做", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107320}, {"id": 252218, "content": "厨房太小 而且收纳做的不合理 找东西费劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199789}, {"id": 250939, "content": "厨房要大", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176704}, {"id": 250942, "content": "永远太小，永远缺调料…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134248}, {"id": 250945, "content": "本来只是想拿个碗泡个面，结果...刷碗擦桌子扫地......", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180448}]}